    {
      "instruction": "<p>Dissolve the <strong>vegetable stock mix</strong> and the <strong>tomato paste</strong> in 300ml <span class=\"text-danger\">[450ml]</span> <strong>boiled water</strong> – this is your<strong> tomato stock</strong></p><p>Drain and rinse the <strong>black beans</strong></p>",
