    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the onion and pepper have softened, increase the heat to medium-high and add the<strong> plant-based mince </strong>with the <strong>ground cumin</strong>, <strong>ground</strong> <strong>smoked paprika</strong>, <strong>dried oregano</strong> and<strong> chilli</strong> <strong>flakes </strong>(can't handle the heat? Go easy!)</p><p>Cook for 3-4 min or until the meat-free mince is browned, breaking it up with a wooden spoon as you go</p>",
