    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the meat-free mince is browned, add the<strong> tomato stock</strong> with the <strong>drained black beans </strong>and <strong>soy sauce</strong> and season with a generous grind of <strong>black pepper</strong></p><p>Bring to the boil over a high heat and cook for 5-6 min further or until the sauce has thickened to a bolognese-like consistency – this is your <strong>meat-free mince chilli</strong></p><p>Tip: If you like it more saucy add a splash more water!</p>",
